，怎麼這次烏里糊塗到不自己領船，看到渡上野船就上呢？為了避戰亂，當地百姓十室九空，婦女更是嚇得足不出戶，怎會有村姑擺渡？元軍沿河搜索，沿河蘆叢中驚出一隻狐狸跳進水中竄回竄去，元軍始終不能捕獲，於時傳言四起，都說烏里是被妖狐所惑落水而亡，便上報了朝庭。<br />\n後來當地村民把這件糊塗案說成妖狐是南宋末代三公主鬼魂所化，稱之為空靈妖狐，烏里受空靈妖狐迷惑落水而亡。把做事糊塗，亂七八糟，戲稱為烏里單刀。"},{"pid":"dfe043e7e33c8cb0a55a777deb4abd8008c16ee8","tid":554531,"uid":65214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪長期係境外生活"},{"pid":"21634fb86a91b90d36e7fe447654c5719fc48842","tid":554531,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"樓主應該唔係廣東地區人士🤔"},{"pid":"57cf44d3dbed02aebe4ddea6000433f2be39e9e9","tid":554531,"uid":34031,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"我係香港人黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764de48233a75229d9978c8db0975d956ae5260e","tid":554531,"uid":140741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"有無人啊媽會講 「bat 巴你死下」？<br />\n男朋友話無聽過人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c813ff1d64c0e427d6488f2cfc27c02f33a1b98","tid":554531,"uid":12526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764de48233a75229d9978c8db0975d956ae5260e","tid":554531,"uid":140741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"有無人啊媽會講 「bat 巴你死下」？<br />\n男朋友話無聽過人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T18:19:12.000Z","msg":"細個打乒乓波大力抽果下會叫bat波<br />\n我諗應該係大巴大巴車到你死死下掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未聽過呢句"},{"pid":"505f0d65270b8de032cd3159052b3ef0f162e2d1","tid":554531,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6c813ff1d64c0e427d6488f2cfc27c02f33a1b98","tid":554531,"uid":12526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764de48233a75229d9978c8db0975d956ae5260e","tid":554531,"uid":140741,"like"